<ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left:5px;"><b><li>Payment terms for Flexxi Promoters</b>:<p>
    Flexxi Promoters book a full taxi for their trip and offer to sell unused seats in their hired taxi. As a Flexxi Promoter you are liable to pay for the full taxi fare for the trip. You shall receive credits for unused seats in your taxi that are purchased by other Flexxi riders for their use. You may choose to apply these credits towards your total booking amount or maybe credited into your Gozo account as Gozo coins for redemption at a future date. You agree to pay your entire due amount in advance before the start of the Flexxi shared trip. Your trip may be subject to cancellation with no refund if we have not received your remaining payment atleast 12 hours before the start of the trip.</li></ul> 
<ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left:5px;"><b><li>Payment terms for Flexxi subscribers</b>:</li><p> 
    <li>Flexxi subscribers can book one or more available seats that are offered by the Flexxi Promoter in a taxi that is booked by the Flexxi Promoter. As Flexxi subscriber, you shall pay in advance for the full fare of Flexxi shared seats you purchase at time of the booking.</li> 
    <li>Pickup address for Flexxi subscriber. You will be providing us your preferred pickup address at the time of creation of your booking. We will use this address to determine the most convenient pickup point where you will join other Flexxi  Riders to start your trip. We will provide you a 15minute time-window for arriving at the pickup point atleast 8hours before your pickup timme. You agree to travel to such pickup point for joining other co-riders.</li><p> 
<ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left:5px;"><b><li>Baggage allowance:</b></li><p>
    <li>As a Flexxi share trip traveler you are allowed only to carry with you 1 personal luggage such as a shoulder bag, backpack, laptop bag or other small item whose dimensions are limited to are 10 inches x 12 inches x 18 inches and weight not exceeding 10kgs 
    Cancellation Policy. You may cancel your booking with us any time before your scheduled date and time of pickup. This may be done using the Gozo Mobile App / Website by logging with your registered credentials or by calling us anytime on the 24x7 Customer Care Helpline +91 90518-77-000.</li><p></ul>
<ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left:5px;"> 
    <li>However, you may be liable to pay cancellation charges under the following circumstances:
        <li>•  If your booking is cancelled within 12 (Twelve) hours of the scheduled pickup date and time, it shall be treated as a No-Show by the Customer. No refund shall be applicable in such cases and the entire Booking Amount/Advance shall be treated as Cancellation Charges.</li>
        <li>•  If your booking is cancelled prior to between 12 & 24 hours of the scheduled pickup date and time, a Cancellation Charge equivalent to 25% of the Booking Amount or the actual Advance amount received from the Customer, whichever is less, shall be applicable. The balance, if any, shall be returned to the Customer within 21 working days.</li>
        <li>•  If you are not present at the scheduled pickup address (in case of Flexxi promoter) or pickup point (in case of Flexxi subscribers) then the driver will wait for you for a maximum of 15minutes, after which we will consider it to be a “NO-SHOW” situation (you have not shown up for your scheduled trip) and the trip will continue without you. Your trip will be considered cancelled with no refund due.</li><p>
<ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left:5px;">
<li><b>Security:</b><p></li>
    <li>Flexxi Promoters and Flexxi subscribers share the ride during a Gozo FLEXXI SHARE trip. You agree to be respectful of your co-riders. At the time of booking your Flexxi share trip, you shall be required to share with us your social identity, gender, age and contact information on the Gozo Platfrom. You agree to grant us the permission to share your social identity and name with your co-riders. If any of the co-riders or driver requires you to produce your identification, you agree to provide such Government issued photo-identification to Gozo for verification before the of the trip and / or to the driver for verification at the start of the trip. In addition, you are required to have a Government issued identification with you at the time of the trip. Your driver or co-riders may refuse to ride with you if you fail to produce such identification. If we for any reason, suspect that you have booked a Gozo Flexxi Share by falsifying your identify or if you are unable to produce identification that matches the traveler name on your booking, you shall not be allowed to continue your ride and your trip shall be cancelled with no refund.</li><p>
